{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fa516b4951","title":"关于党员和团员的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4284852cbb","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"fa516b4951"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5675cd5914","name":"王士勇"},{"id":"85c9c113d9","name":"卢犹崇"},{"id":"879a0e7312","name":"吕庆仕"},{"id":"9004efa26e","name":"王金章"},{"id":"c46d1881e3","name":"朱庭训"},{"id":"ea25ac8f66","name":"西北农学院"},{"id":"ff13b755e7","name":"周明灿"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a392d0c7e2","type":"title","text":"关于党员和团员的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fa516b4951"},{"id":"a41894b5d4","type":"authors","text":"西北农学院周明灿朱庭训王金章吕庆仕卢犹崇王士勇","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fa516b4951"},{"id":"a68d93fdcb","type":"paragraph","text":"“党员是第一等的独裁，一手遮天，弄得十分恐怖。”(林58级学生　周明灿)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fa516b4951"},{"id":"ac68ceaf7d","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)党员为第一等人。(2)老团员是第二等人。(3)新团员是第三等人。(4)同学为第四等人。(林58级学生　周明灿)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fa516b4951"},{"id":"4a757a962a","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党员享的特权多，吃的苦头少，党员在法律上应和大家一律平等。”(园59级学生　朱庭训)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fa516b4951"},{"id":"b630ea7d9b","type":"paragraph","text":"“入党有个正门，有个邪门。邪门容易进去，只要会摇尾巴就可以进去。”(水58级学生　王金章)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fa516b4951"},{"id":"48b8df19e2","type":"paragraph","text":"“团是教条主义的尾巴，团员是吕顺毛。”(植60级学生  吕庆仕)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fa516b4951"},{"id":"2d866395bd","type":"paragraph","text":"“党对党团员太信任了，对非党团员不信任。”“我认为只有会溜须拍马的人才能入团。”(农60级学生　卢犹崇)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fa516b4951"},{"id":"f972491570","type":"paragraph","text":"10．“斯大林说共产党员是特殊材料制成的，难道郭沫若、高尔基不是特殊材料制成的吗？这是造成党群关系上有‘墙’和‘沟’的原因。”(化58级学生　王士勇)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fa516b4951"},{"id":"8027d310b1","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《西北农学院右派言论及错误言论汇集》(西北农学院马列主义教研组编印，1957年12月)。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fa516b4951"}],"page":{"id":"62c9120ce0","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fa516b4951","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}